HEADWORD: magnetic field strength
<hw>magnetic field strength</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The amount of
magnetic flux in a unit area perpendicular to the direction of magnetic
flow.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> magnetic intensity, magnetic induction, magnetic
flux density.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

